0.06     2017-03-10

- SQL migrations will now terminate on the first error in the script rather
  continuing on error. Closes RT #120488.


0.05     2015-07-28

- Added support for all missing createdb options: --locale, --lc-collate,
  --lc-ctype, --tablespace, and --template.


0.04     2013-06-16

- Provide the _driver_name sub needed by the latest Database::Migrator::Core.


0.03     2013-04-06

- Added a compilation test to make CPAN testers happy.


0.02     2013-04-02

- Improved documentation.


0.01     2013-04-01

- First release upon an unsuspecting world.
